(90403, 4, 0, 'I think I understand why this is not working.', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 92244, 'Allari the Souleater to Player'),
(90403, 5, 0, 'A powerful demon I have kept trapped in the gems is helping them to resist.', 12, 0, 100, 273, 0, 0, 92246, 'Allari the Souleater to Player'),
(90403, 6, 0, '$p, you must enter the soul gem and force Arev\'naal to reveal Lord Illidan\'s location.', 12, 0, 100, 397, 0, 0, 92245, 'Allari the Souleater to Player'),
(90406, 0, 0, 'Very good! Off to Zarkhenar, then. Off to see all my friends and family and loved ones.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 39397, 92883, 'Runas the Shamed to Player'),
(90406, 1, 0, '...to kill them, of course, for harming your dragon.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 52845, 92884, 'Runas the Shamed to Player'),
(90406, 2, 0, 'Bunch of mana addicts, that lot, ha hah! Not me, though. My discipline is iron.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 52818, 92885, 'Runas the Shamed to Player'),
(90406, 3, 0, 'Ooh! Mana crystal. Just a moment.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 52839, 92886, 'Runas the Shamed to Player'),
(90406, 4, 0, 'So... why are you here in Azsuna, friend? Just visiting, or...?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 52833, 92887, 'Runas the Shamed to Player'),
(90406, 5, 0, 'My apologies, good dragon. Ahh, look! We are here.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 52837, 92889, 'Runas the Shamed to Player'),
(90474, 0, 0, 'We will work together to destroy the Legion from within.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 56344, 92242, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 1, 0, 'Illidari, what happened here?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57181, 92248, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 2, 0, 'They have all been tortured.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57182, 92243, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 3, 0, 'What did they do? What did the demons offer you?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57183, 92239, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 4, 0, 'Who did this to you?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57184, 92240, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 5, 0, 'Did anyone give in?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57185, 92241, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 6, 0, 'Where did Cyana Nightglaive go? I need to find her!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57186, 93003, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 7, 0, 'A warden working for the Legion? I look forward to killing her.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 57187, 93021, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
(90474, 8, 0, 'You will soon be free, drake.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 56984, 93025, 'Kor\'vas Bloodthorn to Player'),
