(91184, 1, 0, 'You will pay for this betrayal!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 93329, 'Sharazaan'),
(91185, 0, 0, 'Ah... my \'former\' master. Minion! Kill it!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 93327, 'Daglop to Player'),
(91185, 1, 0, 'You failed, \'master\'! Who\'s the master now?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 93328, 'Daglop to Sharazaan'),
(91402, 0, 0, 'Farondis! My most loyal subject. It\'s been too long.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 52897, 93453, 'Vision of Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91402, 1, 0, 'I\'m sorry, you must not recognize me.', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 52896, 93455, 'Vision of Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91402, 2, 0, 'Is this better?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 52898, 93457, 'Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91402, 3, 0, 'Poor, deluded Farondis. Don\'t you remember? I quashed your rebellion ten thousand years ago. Do you remember how powerless you were to stop me?', 12, 0, 100, 25, 0, 52894, 93459, 'Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91402, 4, 0, 'And look at you now! A spectre of your former self, cursed to an eternity of undeath and ineptitude.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 62548, 114140, 'Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91402, 5, 0, 'I\'m giving you an opportunity to kneel before me, princeling. Maybe something can be done about that little curse...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 62549, 114141, 'Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91402, 6, 0, 'Ha ha ha haaa... my wrath is coming.', 12, 0, 100, 15, 0, 52895, 93462, 'Queen Azshara to Player'),
(91419, 0, 0, 'Welcome to our humble place of business, traveler.', 12, 0, 100, 2, 0, 40019, 92192, 'Mr. Shackle to Player'),
(91419, 1, 0, 'It\'s unfortunate that affairs have come to this, but what are we going to do? Wait for them to come slaughter us in our sleep and go out of business?', 12, 0, 100, 6, 0, 0, 111167, 'Mr. Shackle to Player'),
